**Story**
Once upon a time in a forest there lived a monkey who resided on a berry tree which was on the bank of 
a river and in the same forest there also lived a crocodile and his wife..

One day the crocodile came to the bank of the river and rested under the tree. The kind gearted monkey
offered him some fruits. The crocodile came back the next day for more fruits as he loved them. As days
passed by the crocodile and the monkey bacame good friends.  
One day the monkey sent some fruits for the crocodile's wife. She ate the fruits and liked them but was jelous
and she didnt' liked her husband spending time with the monkey she told her husband, "If the fruits are so juicy,
I wonder how sweet the monkey's heart would be. Get me the heart of the monkey". The crocodile was not willing to
kill his friend but have no choice 